reviewText: I already had the cd's, now to have the dvd is just out of sight. On the money. A great buy at a great price. 2 Thumbs up.

A nice collection, but this time only 12 artists...??!!??

Out of which 3 or 4 (I don't remember exactely...) are music videos!!!

I expected all of them being live performances...

But it still sounds nice!!
